In our books, feeding a child from yourself has a number of spiritual benefits including an impact on the child’s manners, faith and overall nature (as given by the mother). Hadith recommends to feed the child for 2 years as long as this doesn’t pose any risk to the mother or child. In fact, we have a hadith that says that the breastfeeding mother has been likened to one who fights for Allah SWT, and if she dies during this time, she attains the reward of a martyr (check out al-Islam.org for more info). 

But as amazing as it is when breastfeeding comes easy to you, this isn’t the case for everyone. There are many women in our community who struggle with breastfeeding, and most of the time it’s out of our control. Conditions such as PCOS or other hormonal imbalances can mean that the woman’s body simply doesn’t produce enough milk, so she has to supplement with formula. Sometimes it’s due to the baby’s temperament as some have a hard time latching, can be born with a tongue tie, or simply get frustrated easily. Having a c-section can also sometimes lead to difficulties when breastfeeding as your body struggles to recover after having major surgery. Pre-term birth, as well as having postpartum depression after birth, can also contribute to difficulties when mothers want to breastfeed. With or without these complications, some women may just choose to opt for formula feeding, and rightfully so. 

Our community puts a lot of pressure on new mothers to breastfeed. And let’s be honest, there is this silent competition among us women as to who is nursing their child and who is doing it the longest... (continued in comments)...";}i:121;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:2;}i:122;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:3;}i:123;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEu4dsWA_y3";}i:124;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:249:"https://scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/118767744_317262722883253_9041959930642353472_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=101&_nc_ohc=C5ROe-03BMMAX9pj5Zw&oh=90e78c0cb3971715c0c35fffbca35e6c&oe=5F7BE62D";}i:125;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:7:"sidecar";}i:126;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:4526009995;}i:127;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:128;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:129;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:130;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391096482718542040";}i:131;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEu4ZUcH-jY";}i:132;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599260934;}i:133;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:662:"NAVY 

